#: static/build.html:194
msgid ""
"The Android Open Source Project build system is designed to provide reliable"
" and reproducible builds. To accomplish this, it provides a prebuilt "
"toolchain and other utilities fulfilling most of the build dependency "
"requirements itself. These prebuilt tools have reproducible builds "
"themselves. It runs the build process within a loose sandbox to avoid "
"accidental dependencies on the host system. The process of moving to a fully"
" self-contained build process with minimal external dependencies is gradual "
"and there are still dependencies that need to be installed on the host "
"system."
msgstr ""

