#: static/hiring.html:41
msgid ""
"We are seeking a highly skilled and self-directed developer to contribute to"
" our open source project, someone who shares our passion for enhancing the "
"privacy and security of mobile devices. The ideal candidate will have "
"experience working with Android-based operating systems, the Linux kernel "
"and its hardening, memory allocators, or extensive experience in Android app"
" development. In this role, you will play a key role in the development and "
"maintenance of our "
msgstr ""

#: static/hiring.html:41
msgid "existing projects"
msgstr ""

#: static/hiring.html:41
msgid ""
", and will be expected to commit a minimum of 80 hours per month. The role "
"will require a high level of autonomy and the ability to independently "
"manage workloads."
