msgstr ""

#: static/hiring.html:45
msgid ""
"Manage a specific aspect of the project, such as the kernel, memory "
"allocator, custom OS features, or apps like Vanadium, Auditor, Camera, or "
"PDF Viewer. Your time will be spent improving them, porting them to new "
"Android versions, reviewing code contributions etc."
msgstr ""

