#: static/hiring.html:69
msgid "About GrapheneOS"
msgstr ""

#: static/hiring.html:70
msgid ""
"GrapheneOS is a privacy and security-focused mobile OS with Android app "
"compatibility developed as a non-profit open source project. It's focused on"
" the research and development of privacy and security technology, including "
"substantial improvements to sandboxing, exploit mitigations, and the "
"permission model. It was founded in 2014 and was formerly known as "
"CopperheadOS. In 2023, the GrapheneOS Foundation was established as a non-"
"profit to help steward development over the long term."
msgstr ""

