"Even though proprietary functionality is needed, eSIM management on GrapheneOS \n"
"                doesn't require any dependency on Google Play, and it never shares data to Google \n"
"                Play even when installed. It won't connect to a Google service unless the carrier \n"
"                uses one themselves."
