#: static/usage.html:1042
msgid ""
"Android Auto requires privileged access in order to work. GrapheneOS uses\n"
"                an extension of the sandboxed Google Play compatibility layer to make Android\n"
"                Auto work with a reduced level of privileges."
msgstr ""

#: static/usage.html:1045
msgid ""
"To install Android Auto, use the GrapheneOS App Store. Android Auto\n"
"                can't be installed through the Play Store or other app sources. Android Auto\n"
"                depends on sandboxed Google Play, you'll be prompted to install it if it's not\n"
