#: static/usage.html:1050
msgid ""
"\n"
"                configuration screen, which contains permission toggles, links to related\n"
"                configuration screens, configuration tips, and links to optional Android Auto\n"
"                dependencies. To set up Android Auto in Private Space, go to "
