#: static/usage.html:1058
msgid ""
"By default, Android Auto is not granted any kind of privileged access. It's\n"
"                treated the same way other apps are treated."
msgstr ""

#: static/usage.html:1060
msgid ""
"In order to work, Android Auto has to be granted baseline permissions for wired\n"
"                or wireless Android Auto. Wired Android Auto requires far less access than wireless\n"
"                Android Auto does. Baseline permissions are controlled by the \"Allow permissions\n"
"                for wired/wireless Android Auto\" toggles."
