#: static/usage.html:1064
msgid ""
"For some cars, baseline permissions for wireless Android Auto are needed even\n"
"                when using wired Android Auto. Therefore, if wired Android Auto is unable to\n"
"                connect to the car with only wired permissions granted, try granting wireless\n"
"                permissions instead."
