#: static/install/cli.html:102
msgid ""
"You need a computer for running the CLI install process with at least 2GB of free\n"
"                memory available and 32GB of free storage space. The web installer can be run on an\n"
"                Android phone or tablet, unlike the command-line installation."
msgstr ""

#: static/install/cli.html:105 static/install/web.html:116
msgid ""
"You need a USB cable for attaching the device to the computer performing the\n"
"                installation. Whenever possible, use the high quality standards compliant USB-C\n"
"                cable packaged with the device. If your computer doesn't have any USB-C ports,\n"
"                you'll need a high quality USB-C to USB-A cable. You should avoid using a USB hub\n"
"                such as the front panel on a desktop computer case. Connect directly to a rear port\n"
"                on a desktop or the ports on a laptop. Many widely distributed USB cables and hubs\n"
"                are broken and are the most common source of issues for installing GrapheneOS."
msgstr ""
"Necesitas un cable USB para conectar el dispositivo al ordenador desde el "
"que se realiza la instalación. Siempre que sea posible, utiliza el cable "
"USB-C de alta calidad y conforme a los estándares incluido con el "
"dispositivo. Si tu ordenador no tiene puertos USB-C, necesitarás un cable "
"USB-C a USB-A de alta calidad. Debes evitar usar un concentrador USB como el"
" panel frontal de una torre de sobremesa. Conéctalo directamente a un puerto"
" trasero en un equipo de sobremesa o a los puertos de un portátil. Muchos "
"cables USB y hubs muy extendidos están defectuosos y son la fuente más común"
" de problemas al instalar GrapheneOS."

#: static/install/cli.html:112 static/install/web.html:123
msgid ""
"Installing from an OS in a virtual machine is not recommended. USB passthrough\n"
"                is often not reliable. To rule out these problems, install from an OS running on\n"
"                bare metal. Virtual machines are also often configured to have overly limited\n"
"                memory and storage space."
msgstr ""
"No se recomienda instalar desde un sistema operativo dentro de una máquina "
"virtual. El passthrough USB suele no ser fiable. Para descartar estos "
"problemas, instala desde un sistema operativo que se ejecute directamente "
"sobre el hardware. Las máquinas virtuales también suelen estar configuradas "
"con una cantidad demasiado limitada de memoria y espacio de almacenamiento."

