#: static/install/cli.html:386 static/install/web.html:298
msgid ""
"Locking the bootloader is important as it enables full verified boot. It also\n"
"                prevents using fastboot to flash, format or erase partitions.  Verified boot will\n"
"                detect modifications to any of the OS partitions and it will prevent reading any\n"
"                modified or corrupted data. If changes are detected, error correction data is used\n"
"                to attempt to obtain the original data at which point it's verified again which\n"
"                makes verified boot robust to non-malicious corruption."
msgstr ""

