"On Android, disable desktop mode for the browser since it currently prevents our\n"
"                web installer from detecting Android and handling needing to request permission to\n"
"                reconnect to the device after each reboot. Desktop mode is enabled by default on\n"
"                large tablets with at least 8GB of RAM such as the Pixel Tablet."
msgstr ""

#: static/install/web.html:165
msgid ""
"You should avoid Flatpak and Snap versions of browsers, as they're known to "
"cause issues during the installation process."
msgstr ""
"Debes evitar las versiones Flatpak y Snap de los navegadores, ya que se sabe"
" que causan problemas durante el proceso de instalación."

#: static/install/web.html:166
msgid "Make sure your browser is up-to-date before proceeding."
msgstr "Asegúrate de que tu navegador esté actualizado antes de continuar."

#: static/install/web.html:167
msgid ""
"Do not use Incognito or other private browsing modes. These modes usually\n"
"                prevent the web installer from having enough storage space to extract the\n"
"                downloaded release."
msgstr ""

